title: 2 Bed 2 Bath Corner Unit w/ Balcony - In the New One Chicago Building
posting_body: ['Stunning 2 Bedroom 2 Bathroom Unit for rent in the new One Chicago Apartment Complex.', 'The building is brand new and offers first class amenities from top to bottom.', '- Corner Unit - Floor to ceiling windows with a private balcony.', '- Includes a membership for each tenant to LifeTime Fitness, which is in the building.', 'This includes a massive pool deck, full gym, classes, sauna, steam room, and more.', '- 1100 sq ft.', '- Similar units in this complex are renting for much more.', '- Valet parking (not included).', 'Package delivery.', '- Pets are allowed - There is a 3000 sq ft dog park in the building on the 10th floor.', '- Utilities are $200 / month, but include high speed internet.', 'Tenant pays ComEd.', 'Available August 15th.', '8 month lease w/ option to extend.']
